ğŸ§  Model Information

The classifier is a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) built using TensorFlow/Keras.
To improve accuracy, it uses Transfer Learning from the VGG16 model (pre-trained on ImageNet):

ğŸ” Steps used:

Freeze early VGG16 layers

Add custom classification layers

Train on MRI tumor dataset

Achieved high accuracy after fine-tuning

ğŸ“Œ Future Enhancements

Add Grad-CAM visual explanations

